processing_metadata.description: Official South Carolina DMV processing rules and validation requirements

global_rules.code_system: Information needed - research plate type code system
global_rules.character_restrictions: Does not use letter 'O' on standard plates - only number zero '0'; State does not use letter 'O', only number '0'; Uses the letter 'O' when it is shaped like an 'o'. Example tags: SC-BC3056CC (stacked must be keyed), SC-EA354, VT00000, SC-ZD00000 (stacked must be keyed). Stacked characters must be keyed.

stacked_characters.position: Y- Omit verticals at end.; Y - Vertical characters must be verified as seen.; Y- Key Verticals
stacked_characters.notes: Stacked characters MUST be keyed (e.g., SC-BC3056CC, SC-EA354, SC-ZD00000); Extracted from 18 plate types with character modifications
